                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220911-303-victim2704 t18220911-303-viclabel1588"></join>. On Sunday afternoon, the 15th of September, I met the prisoner about half-past two o'clock in Covent-garden - I went to <placeName id="t18220911-303-crimeloc1589">No. 4, Leg-alley</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18220911-303-crimeloc1589" type="placeName" value="No. 4, Leg-alley"></interp>
