                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220911-303-off1586 t18220911-303-crimeloc1589"></join>, with her. I fell asleep in a few minutes, and awoke again in ten minutes. I missed my watch, my purse, and money, which were safe when I went to the house. I had been taking rum and water, which affected me a little.</p>
